### Generate SVG Path for Custom Bar Shape - Recharts

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/Customise.mdx

Creates a curved SVG path string for rendering custom bar shapes. Takes x, y coordinates and width, height dimensions to generate a smooth curved path using cubic Bézier curves. Used as shape property in Bar components.

```javascript
export const getPath = (x, y, width, height) => (
  `M${x},${y + height}
   C${x + width / 3},${y + height} ${x + width / 2},${y + height / 3} ${x + width / 2}, ${y}
   C${x + width / 2},${y + height / 3} ${x + 2 * width / 3},${y + height} ${x + width}, ${y + height}
   Z`
);
```

